name: Dengar With Blaster Carbine (V)
Lore: 'Corellian bounty hunter. Skilled athlete. Expert shot. Has worked many times for Jabba the Hutt. Carries a long-standing grudge against Han Solo.',
Text: 'While opponent''s [Reflections II] objective on table, adds one battle destiny.  Permanent weapon is •Blaster Carbine (twice per battle, may target a character or vehicle for free; draw destiny; target ''hit,'' and its forfeit = 0, if destiny +1 > defense value).',
